> * if you choose `I already use Status` **you can only sync your device with another one** (no option to use your seed)

@qoqobolo this is only because this hasn't been built yet, it's all in the designs.  When more of the mobile onboarding designs are built, mobile will become functionally aligned with desktop here.

The issue is that desktop has all the required onboarding functionality, and currently mobile has only built a subset of the required onboarding functionality.
